In[16]:
import geopandas as gpd

country=gpd.read_file(australiaMapsLink,layer='country')
cities=gpd.read_file(australiaMapsLink,layer='cities')
rivers=gpd.read_file(australiaMapsLink,layer='rivers')
centroid=gpd.read_file(australiaMapsLink,layer='centroid')
airports=gpd.read_file(australiaMapsLink,layer='airports')

Let's turn those points into projected spatial object (GDF of points):

In[20]:
seaports=gpd.GeoDataFrame(data=infoseaports.copy(),
                           geometry=gpd.points_from_xy(infoseaports.Longitude,
                                                       infoseaports.Latitude),
                          crs=4326)
seaports_australia=seaports[seaports['Country Code']=='Australia'].copy()
seaports_australia.reset_index(drop=True, inplace=True)
seaports_australia_3112=seaports_australia.to_crs(3112)
